    </action>
    <action datetime="1999-10-21T19:22:00-05:00">
      <text>GENERAL DEBATE - The Committee of the Whole proceeded with two hours of general debate on H.R. 2300.</text>
    </action>
    <action datetime="1999-10-21T21:33:00-05:00">
      <text>DEBATE - Pursuant to H. Rept. 106-408, the Committee is debating the amendment offered by Mr. Fattah for 20 minutes.</text>
